    qA{Need the button to remember a state}
    qB{Are the options mutually exclusive}
    qC{Need a one-shot command}

    qC -->|Yes| ansA[Use JButton]
    qA -->|No| ansA
    qA -->|Yes| qB
    qB -->|No| ansB[Use JCheckBox independent selection]
    qB -->|Yes| ansC[Use JRadioButton inside a ButtonGroup]
```
